cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MA 

The paper discusses the deployment and operation of UAV-aided mobile services, which involves wireless communication and network optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses economic issues related to the deployment and operation of the UAV network, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) or cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses algorithmic game theory, which further supports the possibility of it belonging to cs.GT. The paper also discusses energy consumption and cooperation among UAVs, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
